{"_id":"1ZXTHggEGDhm31KT","name":"Shibboleth","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Shibboleth</p>\n<p>3rd Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>Choose any number of creatures.</p>\n<p>For as long as this spell is ongoing, creatures you didn&rsquo;t choose can&rsquo;t understand words spoken by whoever you chose, even by magical means.</p>\n<p><strong>While this spell is ongoing, you take -1 to cast a spell.</strong></p>","spellLevel":3,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"2QQ2Nu5adOuVReAY","name":"Wordsmith","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Wordsmith</p>\n<p>When you have access to a forge and holy instruments, you can inscribe Words of Power on weapons, armor, and other objects permanently.</p>\n<p>The GM will tell you the effect produced.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"3FnOT2srxz1UdyRj","name":"Rune Savant","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Rune Savant</p>\n<p>You learn another Word of Power.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"3W1uU1sm5l0K6rzl","name":"Power Word Stun","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Power Word Stun</p>\n<p>9th Level</p>\n<p>You speak the word of stillness, and all creatures that hear you cannot move.</p>\n<p>The effect ends when any affected creature takes damage, or you end the spell</p>","spellLevel":9,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7ovf2a8ZK4dC2VkH","name":"Flamestrike","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Flamestrike</p>\n<p>5th Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>A column of divine flame erupts upwards from a target nearby. All creatures in the area take [[/r 2d6]] damage.</p>\n<p>This damage ignores armor.</p>\n<p><strong>While the spell is ongoing, the column persists, and you take -1 to cast a spell.</strong></p>","spellLevel":5,"rollFormula":"2d6","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"8GtXv2Kqgplumcv9","name":"Calm","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Calm</p>\n<p>5th Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>[[/r 2d4]] creatures of the GM&rsquo;s choice are made calm.</p>\n<p>They will refrain from violence, although their disposition towards you does not change.</p>\n<p>This spell lasts until any one of those creatures is attacked or takes damage.</p>\n<p>While this spell is ongoing, you take -1 to cast a spell.</p>","spellLevel":5,"rollFormula":"2d4","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"9XIFs25MIMf2ijXG","name":"Empower","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Empower</p>\n<p>When you Cast a Spell, on a 10+, you have the option from choosing from the 7-9 list. If you do, you choose one of these effects as well</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The spell&rsquo;s effects are doubled</li>\n<li>The spell&rsquo;s targets are doubled</li>\n</ul>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"C8EwLm1g546Ox5Bu","name":"Linguist","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Linguist</p>\n<p>Choose a spell from any class list. You can cast that spell as though it were one l evel lower.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"CBuYH3SWVZCoI3VO","name":"Tongue And Hands Of The Runekeeper","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Tongue And Hands Of The Runekeeper</p>\n<p>Your spoken and written words transcend language. Any sapient creature or entity that can understand language will understand you.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"FPmgWqY0TYjVve3V","name":"Identify","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Identify</p>\n<p>3rd Level</p>\n<p>Touch an object or creature.</p>\n<p>You learn what magic effects are currently being worked on it or creature or what enchantments it has.</p>","spellLevel":3,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"FXDVtGVN96bA8Rcv","name":"Antimagic Field","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Antimagic Field</p>\n<p>5th Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>As you cast this spell, walk the perimeter of an area.</p>\n<p>As long as you stay within that boundary, spells and magical effects cannot persist in the enclosed field. Magical effects end or are severely dampened.</p>\n<p>Spells cast outside the field have no effect i nside the field. Spells cast within the field automatically fail.</p>\n<p><strong>While this spell is ongoing, you can&rsquo;t cast a spell.</strong></p>","spellLevel":5,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"FqN5QadFY4f53uLV","name":"Command","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Command</p>\n<p>3rd Level</p>\n<p>You speak a one word command to a creature that can hear and understand you.</p>\n<p>The creature obeys to the best of its ability for a brief time or refuses and is temporarily stunned.</p>","spellLevel":3,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"GWMMVtOcUC7Anzvm","name":"Profane Word","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Profane Word</p>\n<p>9th Level</p>\n<p>You speak the word of destruction that foretells the end of days.</p>\n<p>A non-living thing of your choice is removed from existence</p>","spellLevel":9,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"GY5SNttvVMTtbBh8","name":"Celestial Bolt","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Celestial Bolt</p>\n<p>7th Level</p>\n<p>Divine energy bursts forth from you, filling the immediate area.</p>\n<p>All those found wanting take [[/r 2d8]] damage.</p>\n<p>This damage pierces armor.</p>","spellLevel":7,"rollFormula":"2d8","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Gw83Saq9f7Q2eOVL","name":"Prepare Spells","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Prepare Spells</p>\n<p>When you spend uninterrupted time (an hour or so) in quiet contemplation of your lexicon, you:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Lose any spells you already prepared.</li>\n<li>Prepare new spells chosen from your spellbook whose total levels don&rsquo;t exceed your own level +1.</li>\n</ul>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"InESxkh8cfT10yM7","name":"Ghost Writer","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Ghost Writer</p>\n<p>When you have time, safety, and the appropriate arcane materials, you can<strong> inscribe your Words of Power</strong> on a soul, yours or someone else's.</p>\n<p>The GM will tell you the effect produced.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"K0o1knZhlFE2nF5Y","name":"Future Tense","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Future Tense</p>\n<p>When you i nscribe your Words of Power, instead of activating the magic immediately, you may give an activation trigger, such as &ldquo;someone reads it&rdquo; or &ldquo;I speak the command word&rdquo;.</p>\n<p>When the trigger is met, the rune activates.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"KddvmOOwQzrGyWmz","name":"Shield of Faith","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Shield of Faith</p>\n<p>1st Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>One ally you touch is bolstered.</p>\n<p>While the spell is ongoing, that ally has +2 armor, and you take -1 to cast a spell.</p>","spellLevel":1,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"KlOPnzOd1LeLZVGi","name":"Interjection","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Interjection</p>\n<p>When you Aid or Interfere by your words, you take +1, but anyone who can hear you will know you are implicated.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"N5MQYJuWL4J4deIn","name":"Portal","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Portal</p>\n<p>7th Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>You etch a few words, no more than your level, on a surface describing your destination, and a portal to that location appears on that surface.</p>\n<p>The portal can be one- or two-way at your discretion, although the exit portal is not visible.</p>\n<p>The portal lasts for up to a day, although you can end it at any time.</p>\n<p>If you cast this spell again while you have a portal active, that earlier portal closes.</p>","spellLevel":7,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"N92hnger8kMr8LUv","name":"Well Read","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Well Read</p>\n<p>Gain the Bard move Bardic Lore with the Gods and their Servants speciality and one other speciality of your choice.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"NwG0DLVgdHH92LX3","name":"Conjunction Function","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Conjunction Function</p>\n<p>When you inscribe two Words of Power into a combined rune, you can combine their properties.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"OTSh7XOCNv6Nfrb9","name":"Runic Power","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Runic Power</p>\n<p>Replaces: Empower</p>\n<p>When you Cast a Spell, on a 10-11, you have the option from choosing from the 7-9 l ist. If you do, you choose one of these effects as well.</p>\n<p>On a 12+, you get to choose one of these effects for free.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The spell&rsquo;s effects are doubled</li>\n<li>The spell&rsquo;s targets are doubled</li>\n<li>You add the effects of one of your Words of Power to the spell</li>\n</ul>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"Empower","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"P2hruhzVMPfAXxIL","name":"Detect Alignment","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Detect Alignment</p>\n<p>1st Level</p>\n<p>When you cast this spell choose an alignment: Good, Evil, Lawful, or Chaotic.</p>\n<p>One of your senses is briefly able to detect that alignment.</p>\n<p>The GM will tell you what here i s of that alignment.</p>","spellLevel":1,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"P30q6WLeWd3d5YH1","name":"To Edit, Divine","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>To Edit, Divine</p>\n<p>When your ewrite the divine script in a place of power, tell the GM what facet of the world you're trying to change and what words you're doing it with, then Roll+WIS.</p>\n<p>On a 10+, choose one.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, both.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your handwriting is unmistakable, and the gods will come find you.</li>\n<li>Your revision leads to additional unforeseen changes, the GM will tell you what.</li>\n</ul>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"WIS","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"QgLM6LnDBXV4jFiA","name":"The Wise Man’s Fear","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>The Wise Man&rsquo;s Fear</p>\n<p>When you speak aloud someone's true name ( you must know it, first), roll+WIS.</p>\n<p>On a hit, you grasp their very essence and can do with them as you will.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, choose one:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Their God/s, masters, peers, and/or servants are angered.</li>\n<li>Their soul resists, and your hold is not strong.</li>\n<li>You bind their name and fate to your own.</li>\n</ul>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"WIS","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"QmDANB7DXDapxCfM","name":"Healing Word","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Healing Word</p>\n<p>1st Level - Known: ❏</p>\n<p>By this holy word are you healed. You or one ally within earshot heals [[/r 1d6]] damage.</p>","spellLevel":1,"rollFormula":"1d6","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"TGISlZVVdUSUbvWr","name":"Heat/Chill Metal","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Heat/Chill Metal</p>\n<p>1st Level - Ongoing - Known: ❏</p>\n<p>At your touch, a piece of metal becomes unbearably hot or cold. Held items are likely abandoned. Larger objects are uncomfortable to be around.</p>\n<p>While this spell is ongoing, you take -1 to cast a spell.</p>","spellLevel":1,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"UKSTKpbxKWQwRMys","name":"Fire And Brimstone","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Fire And Brimstone</p>\n<p>When you i ncite the faithful to action by their beliefs, speak the relevant precept of their faith and roll+CHA.</p>\n<p>On a 10+, it catches, and your congregation will follow your will.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, a number of them agree, but some of the flock have other ideas.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"CHA","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"V38D2zSdL7ixFmvL","name":"Rune of Protection","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Rune of Protection</p>\n<p>1st Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>You walk the pattern of a rune in the ground around an area.</p>\n<p>Until you prepare spells again, you are alerted when any creature that wishes you harm enters the area, and any such creatures take [[/r 1d4]] damage when they enter the area.</p>","spellLevel":1,"rollFormula":"1d4","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Y6IYWVEzozHrbcKJ","name":"True Knowing","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>True Knowing</p>\n<p>9th Level</p>\n<p>You speak the word of knowing and touch a person or object.</p>\n<p>You learn everything that person knows, or knew if they are dead.</p>\n<p>If you touched an object this way, you see or experience events from that object&rsquo;s perspective to learn the relevant i nformation.</p>","spellLevel":9,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"YqbcfjtjWbyeZ0yv","name":"Enshrine","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Enshrine</p>\n<p>When you mark a storied place with a <strong>Word of Power</strong>, it becomes a place of power. Name the divine force to whom this place will be attuned.</p>\n<p>The GM will tell you who or what else is interested and/or to whom this place used to belong.</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ZVcF9QjvwwuV9Cuc","name":"Divine Word","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Divine Word</p>\n<p>9th Level</p>\n<p>You speak the word of creation, the word that made the world.</p>\n<p>Creatures and things in the area that are anathema to the divine are remade to be more pleasing.</p>","spellLevel":9,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"cSsO4gjpakBPTFVa","name":"Cast A Spell","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Cast A Spell (WIS)</p>\n<p>When you r elease a spell you&rsquo;ve prepared, roll+WIS.</p>\n<p>On a 10+ the spell i s successfully cast and you may cast the spell again l ater.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9 the spell i s cast, but choose one:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You draw unwelcome attention or put yourself i n a spot. The GM will tell you how.</li>\n<li>The spell disturbs the fabric of reality as it is cast; take -1 ongoing to cast a spell until the next time you Prepare Spells.</li>\n<li>After it is cast, the spell i s forgotten. You cannot cast the spell again until you Prepare Spells.</li>\n</ul>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"WIS","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"dEZvs97YDWKP63fO","name":"Greater Mending","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Greater Mending</p>\n<p>7th Level</p>\n<p>You inscribe a few runes on an i nanimate object and it is repaired, like new, to i ts original form.</p>\n<p>If you write these runes i n blood on a living thing, they heal [[/r 3d8]] damage.</p>","spellLevel":7,"rollFormula":"3d8","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"efJdPNmYF9VFgv6T","name":"Lexicon","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"equipment","data":{"name":"","description":"","class":"","quantity":1,"weight":1,"uses":0,"tags":"","tagsString":"","magic":false,"itemType":"","attributes":{},"rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/sundries/books/book-eye-pink.webp","effects":[]}
{"_id":"i4paPp1M2CyhhaXM","name":"Zone of Truth","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Zone of Truth</p>\n<p>3rd Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>After you cast this spell, you mark the boundary of a small area.</p>\n<p>Within this area, you are alerted of any un- or partial-truths told.</p>\n<p>Weaker minded creatures find it incredibly difficult to lie.</p>\n<p>While this spell i s ongoing, you take -1 to cast a spell.</p>","spellLevel":3,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"jU31aoY8qVhyv9PU","name":"Archon’s Aura","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Archon&rsquo;s Aura</p>\n<p>7th Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>A golden, shining crown appears above your head, radiating divinity while this spell is ongoing.</p>\n<p>Attacks made against you and allies near you deal -[[/r 1d6]] damage until the spell ends.</p>\n<p>Weak willed, ignorant, or evil creatures are compelled to flee, cower, or fight.</p>\n<p><strong>While this spell is ongoing, you take -1 to cast a spell.</strong></p>","spellLevel":7,"rollFormula":"1d6","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"kAfpqUTYTWMTuuM0","name":"Golem","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Golem</p>\n<p>5th Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>Inscribe a rune of your choice i n some substance. That substance becomes a golem that will follow your directions.</p>\n<p>Treat it as a character with access to the basic moves and a +1 in all stats.</p>\n<p>It has HP equal to your l evel.</p>\n<p>Additionally, choose [[/r 1d6]] of these traits.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>It&rsquo;s tough - i t has 3 armor</li>\n<li>It&rsquo;s talented - one of i ts stats has a +2 modifier</li>\n<li>It&rsquo;s especially resistant to magic</li>\n<li>It&rsquo;s powerful - +1 damage and forceful</li>\n<li>Its substance i s malleable and a daptive</li>\n<li>It i sn&rsquo;t slow</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The golem l asts until it is reduced to 0 HP or you end the spell.</p>\n<p><strong>While the spell i s ongoing, you take -1 to cast a spell.</strong></p>","spellLevel":5,"rollFormula":"1d6","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
