{"_id":"ne1jwcnMnTDsPfKU","name":"Summon Angel","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Summon Angel</p>\n<p>9th Level - Ongoing</p>\n<p>You speak the word of calling and summon a denizen of the astral plane, a servant of some deity.</p>\n<p>It will fight for you or do as you command so long as it finds you worthy or until death (yours or its).</p>\n<p>You can have only one angel summoned at a time.</p>\n<p><strong>While this spells is ongoing, you take -1 to cast a spell.</strong></p>","spellLevel":9,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false,"class":"The Runepriest"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
