{"_id":"xOUHHc29qEDijslW","name":"95 Theses","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>95 Theses</p>\n<p>When you write someone a pointed note, letter, or missive, roll+CHA.</p>\n<p>On a hit, you've made yourself understood. Your recipient will challenge you, do as you say, or i gnore you at obvious peril.</p>\n<p>On a 10+ they take it to heart - if they don't act on your words, they are filled with doubt, insecurity or regret.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","class":"The Runepriest","rollType":"CHA","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
